     F*---------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALL PARAMETERS
     F*                    CALL 'AHBR02'
     F*                    PARM           P@MODE  1      IN
     F*                    PARM           P@HIN1  5      IN
     F*                    PARM           P@HIN2  5      IN
     F*                    PARM           P@HIN3  2      IN
     F*  P@MODE=1  --> READ AJZPL31  (KANBAN ISSUE FILE2)
     F*  P@MODE<>1 --> READ AH#TL19  (KANBAN ORDER DATA ACCUMULATION)
