     F* 2017/01/18 | JW (SRA)    | JW4 | REVERCE UNS FIELD            *
     F* 2018/02/23 | JW (SRA)    | JW5 | DISPLAY SORT SCAN DATE/TIME  *
     F* 2018/05/09 | JW (SRA)    | JW6 | FIX A BUG (SRT FIELD COLOR)  *
     F* 2019/02/04 | JW (SRA)    | JW7 | CHG COLOR OF PICKUP DATE     *
     F* 2019/08/21 | JW (SRA)    | JW8 | SET PART TO 1ST SCREEN       *
     F* 2019/09/13 | JW (SRA)    | JW9 | FIX INDEX ISSUE              *
     F* 2019/11/13 | JW (SRA)    | JWA | USE SYSTEM DATE INSTEAD OF *DATE
     F* 2020/04/17 | JW (SRA)    | JWB | CHG APLC11 --> UTLC11        *
     F* 2020/12/09 | TM (DCS)    |     | ADDING F23=AHBR10 CALL       *
